definition.featurexml:
<xml><block type="feature_container" deletable="false" x="40" y="40">
<value name="feature"><block type="feature_custom_structure">
	<field name="structure">erable</field>
	<field name="x">0</field>
	<field name="y">0</field>
	<field name="z">0</field>
	<field name="random_rotation">TRUE</field>
	<field name="random_mirror">TRUE</field>
	<value name="ignored_blocks">
		<block type="block_holderset_list"><mutation inputs="1"></mutation><field name="block0">Blocks.STRUCTURE_BLOCK</field></block>
	</value>
</block>
</value>
<next><block type="placement_rarity">
	<field name="rarity">100</field>
	<next><block type="placement_count">
	<value name="count">
		<block type="int_provider_uniform">
			<field name="min">1</field>
			<field name="max">4</field>
		</block>
	</value>
	<next><block type="placement_in_square"><next><block type="placement_heightmap">
	<field name="heightmap">OCEAN_FLOOR_WG</field>
	<next><block type="placement_block_predicate_filter">
	<value name="condition">
		<block type="block_predicate_matching_blocks">
			<field name="x">0</field>
			<field name="y">-1</field>
			<field name="z">0</field>
			<value name="blockSet">
				<block type="block_holderset_list">
					<mutation inputs="1"></mutation>
					<field name="block0">Blocks.GRASS</field>
				</block>
			</value>
		</block>
	</value>
	<next><block type="placement_biome_filter"></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></xml>
